#: ../../library/decimal.rst:1841
msgid ""
"The number system for the :mod:`decimal` module provides special values "
"including ``NaN``, ``sNaN``, ``-Infinity``, ``Infinity``, and two zeros, "
"``+0`` and ``-0``."
